{
  "stem": "18575.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he says it's very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Be-- be very careful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "While I was on the railroad station, the loudspeaker announced that in track number five-- and I remember it distinctly-- there is a train from Lvov-- Lemberg, of course, in German-- to Warsaw, only for Germans.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I understood Germans from Yiddish a-- a little.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it said, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Do not board this train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This train is only for Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Direct train, Lvov-Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I-- the trains, the Polish trains had steps outside running the full length of the train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I waited till the train start moving.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I jumped on the steps.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And few minutes later, after it left the station, I open the door and walked in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was a empty cabin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I sat down.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Few minutes later-- maybe 10, 20 minutes later-- a German officer came in, sat opposite me, took out his newspaper, open up his attache-- he had a-- a case-- took out a sandwich and start reading, eating.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He didn't introduce himself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I didn't introduce myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We went straight to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Being that the train was free for Germans, there were no conductors.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was no inspection.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he didn't know who I was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I knew, more or less, who he was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Truly, I was a little concerned.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because he wore a brown uniform with a band that says, Todt Organisation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Now Todt, to me, T-O-D-T, meant death organization.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he had a swastika, of course, on his left armband.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You know, Todt was a worker organization, was a labor-- German labor-- things that build bridges.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It's-- the-- it was a German minister, Todt.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And his name was Todt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That was-- anyway.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Just as the train approach Warsaw railroad, I jumped off the train, before it actually stopped.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
